venile Fiction\']',4,20,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=G9s8PgAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(430,'The Complete Short Stories of H.G. Wells','[\'Herbert George Wells\', \'John R. Hammond\']','Phoenix','2000','One of the founding-fathers of science fiction, it is in his short stories that Wells first explored the enormous potential of the scientific discoveries of his age. In this first ever complete collection of his stories, 84 minor miracles of the storyteller\'s art remind us of the relevance of this greatest of modern dreamers.',9781842124024,'[\'Fiction\']',4,3,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=4mS4SAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(431,'The Name of the Rose','[\'Umberto Eco\']','Everyman\'s Library Classics &','2006','In 1327, finding his sensitive mission at an Italian abbey further complicated by seven bizarre deaths, Brother William of Baskerville turns detective, penetrating the cunning labyrinth of the abbey and deciphering coded manuscripts for clues.',9780307264893,'[\'Fiction\']',4,164,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=XY2vXKsHbzIC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api','en'),(432,'In the Name of Jesus','[\'Henri J. M. Nouwen\']','Crossroad Faith & Formation','1992-10-01','Ruminates on the problems, and possible solutions, in today\'s Christian leadership, offering a rethinking of how to lead, one based more firmly on divine guidance',9780824512590,'[\'Religion\']',4.5,16,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=T9ZZOAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(433,'Blood Done Sign My Name','[\'Timothy B. Tyson\']','Broadway Books','2004','The author returns to his hometown of Oxford, North Carolina, to make sense of the thirty-year-old murder of a black man by a Klansman, and the Klansman\'s subsequent acquittal by an all-white jury.',9781400083114,'[\'Biography & Autobiography\']',4.5,8,'http://books.google.com/books/content?