r Wilde seeks Jesus Christ\'s answer in Ravi Zacharias\'s entertaining dialogue.',9781590528600,'[\'Religion\']',5,3,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=TwdwDwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api','en'),(854,'Travels with Charley','[\'John Steinbeck\']','Penguin Group USA','2002','Steinbeck records his emotions and experiences during a journey of rediscovery in his native land.',9780142000700,'[\'Biography & Autobiography\']',4,3294,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=teRKAAAAYAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(855,'Walt Disney\'s the Life and Times of Scrooge McDuck','[\'Don Rosa\']','Gemstone Pub','2005','Don Rosa created this twelve-part story to delineate exactly how Scrooge McDuck acquired his fortune and became the World\'s Richest Duck. The story was originally serialized in the United States in Uncle Scrooge comics. Now it has been collected in one all-encompassing popularly-priced volume.',9780911903966,'[\'Juvenile Fiction\']',5,1,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=JQB0PwAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(856,'Walt Disney\'s the Life and Times of Scrooge McDuck Companion','[\'Don Rosa\']','Gemstone Pub','2006','Stories of Scrooge McDuck\'s early life and adventures, plus commentaries by the author.',9781888472400,'[\'Comics & Graphic Novels\']',5,3,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=yAqOAAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(857,'A Christmas Story','[\'Jean Shepherd\']','Three Rivers Press (CA)','2003','The stories that inspired a popular holiday film chronicle an American family\'s trials and joys in a small town in Depression-era Indiana, capturing Ralphie Potter\'s campaign to get a Red Ryder air rifle for Christmas, his duel with bullies, and other epi',9780767916226,'[\'Fiction\']',4,19,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=z2kgAQAAIAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(858,'My First Story of Ch