','en'),(3011,'Dealing in Futures','[\'Joe Haldeman\']','New Amer Library','1993-11-01','This collection contains eleven of the author\'s finest stories, ranging from faraway planets beyond human comprehension to a nightmare future Earth. By the author of The Forever War. Original.',9780451452580,'[\'Fiction\']',3.5,4,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=Y5sBAAAACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(3012,'Coronado','[\'Dennis Lehane\']','William Morrow','2006-08-08','Presents a compilation of some of the author\'s previously published short works, in a volume that includes an original short tale and the story, Until Gwen.',9780061139673,'[\'Fiction\']',3.5,49,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=JOplAAAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(3013,'Prayers for Rain','[\'Dennis Lehane\']','Harper Collins','2000-05-02','When a former client jumps from the twenty-sixth floor, private investigator Patrick Kenzie digs into her past to uncover the psychopath responsible for her self-destruction.',9780380730360,'[\'Fiction\']',4,23,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=ryrPaNqdW70C&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api','en'),(3014,'A Drink Before the War','[\'Dennis Lehane\']','Houghton Mifflin Harcourt','2003','Private detective partners Patrick Kenzie and Angela Gennaro are hired to find Jenna Angeline, a missing black cleaning woman who allegedly stole confidential state documents, but as their investigation becomes complicated by rival gang leaders, extortion, child prostitution, and assassination reaching to the highest levels of government, they discover that their target has been framed. Reprint. 15,000 first printing.',9780156029025,'[\'Fiction\']',4,34,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=1UQOpInULqUC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api','en'),(3015,'Shutter Island','[\'Dennis Lehane\']','Harper Collins','2004-04-27','U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels and his partner