c, embarks on a dangerous quest to find the truth, a search that leads her to Perkar, a chieftain\'s son who has sworn to destroy the dreaded River God. Reprint.',9780345396709,'[\'Fiction\']',3.5,2,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=JUgi-2zT-7YC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(3895,'Influence','[\'Robert B. Cialdini\']','ICON Group International','2007','Dr Robert Cialdini explains the six psychological principles that drive the human impulse to comply to the pressures of others and reveals how to defend oneself against manipulation.',9780061241895,'[\'Business & Economics\']',4,20,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=E5p5qVbkl1IC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(3896,'Writings, 1902-1910','[\'William James\']','Library of America','1987','Examines the role of religion in human lives, the nature of the universe, truth, pragmatism, war, politics, and metaphysics',9780940450387,'[\'Literary Collections\']',5,1,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=rQquNBaUJ-YC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api','en'),(3897,'Ghost Hunters','[\'Deborah Blum\']','Penguin Group USA','2006','Traces how the respected psychologist brother of Henry James set out to gather scientific data proving the existence of ghosts at the end of the nineteenth century, forming the American Society for Psychical Research.',9781594200908,'[\'Medical\']',4,3,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=_J_YAAAAMAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','en'),(3898,'The Principles of Psychology','[\'William James\']','Harvard University Press','1981','Presents an authoritative new edition of the classic text that corrects hundreds of errors and incorporates all of the changes James made in the eight printings he supervised, along with revisions and new material the author added to his own annotated copy.',9780674705593,'[\'Psychology\']',4,5,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=JKeCfOnHSA8C&printsec=frontcover